# Global Localization Rule

- Every user-facing text change must be translated to all supported languages: `eng`, `esp`, `ru`, `fr`, `it`, `de`, `uk`, `pl`.
- Update related labels, titles, subtitles, descriptions, and modal copy where applicable.
- Keep wording consistent across card/list text and corresponding modal translations.
- Before finishing, verify there are no leftover old strings in any language.

